   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>From the App Launcher, find and open the <uicontrol>Power CLM</uicontrol>
               app.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click the <uicontrol>Agreements</uicontrol> tab from the navigation bar. You can
               perform the same action on the <uicontrol>Proposals</uicontrol> tab in the
                  <uicontrol>Power CPQ</uicontrol> app as well.</p>
            <p>
               <note type="note">
                  <p>Select the appropriate object. You can add a related list to objects like
                     Contacts, Proposals, Opportunities, and more.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Select an agreement and click the <uicontrol>Edit Layout</uicontrol> link.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>From the layout pane, click <uicontrol>Related Lists.</uicontrol>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Drag and drop the appropriate related list to the appropriate location. It is recommended to have eSignatures, Document Versions, and Notes &amp; Attachments related lists in the page layout for agreement or quote/proposal.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Save</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
   </body>
